  <para>
    In this section, you will learn how to create
    simple objects in <acronym>GIMP</acronym>. It's pretty easy once
    you figure out how to do it. <acronym>GIMP</acronym> provides a
    huge set of <link linkend="gimp-toolbox-introduction">Tools</link>
    and Shortcuts which most new users get lost in.
  </para>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  

  <sect2 id="gimp-using-line">
    <title>
      <phrase>Drawing a Straight Line</phrase>
      
      
      
      
      
      
      
    </title>

<!-- Already defined
    <indexterm lang="en">
      <primary>Painting Tools</primary><secondary>Straight Line</secondary>
    </indexterm>
    <indexterm lang="de">
      <primary>Malwerkzeug</primary><secondary>Gerade Linie</secondary>
